{"code": 0, "data": [{"cid": 2951563, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Alice", "pid": 560424, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "按补助发了吧？", "timestamp": 1637024634, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2951571, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Bob", "pid": 560424, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "研究生又不是义务教育，为啥要退你学费?", "timestamp": 1637024684, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2951630, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Carol", "pid": 560424, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "搞的我是去交钱给导师干活", "timestamp": 1637025482, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2951666, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Dave", "pid": 560424, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "非全研究生瑟瑟发抖，学费能买三辆车了。\n甚至是6辆。。。。。（五菱MINIEV）", "timestamp": 1637025915, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2951752, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Bob", "pid": 560424, "reply_to": 2951630, "tag": null, "text": "Re Carol: 你给导师干活，是会有补助的。交学费和领补助是不矛盾的两件事，一码是一码", "timestamp": 1637027090, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2952213, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Eve", "pid": 560424, "reply_to": 2951752, "tag": null, "text": "Re Bob: 研究生校补助了解一下，硕士每个月1227，博士每个月2810，这就是把你交的学费学费退给你另外再给你补了一些钱", "timestamp": 1637031624, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2952455, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Bob", "pid": 560424, "reply_to": 2952213, "tag": null, "text": "Re Eve: 对啊，补助是补助，学费是学费。有的专业不需要给导师干活，就没有补助或者补助比较少；有的专业有的学生给导师干的活比较多，补助就比较多。", "timestamp": 1637033592, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2952505, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Carol", "pid": 560424, "reply_to": 2952213, "tag": null, "text": "Re Eve: 我就是硕士生，我的补助560，哪有1227这么多。560×12等于多少呢", "timestamp": 1637034107, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2953115, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Eve", "pid": 560424, "reply_to": 2952505, "tag": null, "text": "Re Carol: 北京这边的全日制学硕学校发放都是1227一个月，如果少了，要么你不是清华的全日制，要么你们院里发放出了问题，可以打电话直接找研究生院问，这是全校统一标准。", "timestamp": 1637038880, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2953128, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Eve", "pid": 560424, "reply_to": 2952455, "tag": null, "text": "Re Bob: 我觉得你可能是语言理解有问题。连校补助和导师补助都分不清楚？校补助是学校走研究生院直接发给每个清华脱产全日制研究生的。至于导师给你发多少关校补助什么事？你就是没导师，不给导师干活，只要你是在学状态就有这笔钱", "timestamp": 1637038992, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2953144, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Eve", "pid": 560424, "reply_to": 2952455, "tag": null, "text": "Re Bob: 校补助就是你的学费按月返还，然后加上一些北京市和学校的补贴。另外一部分是导师补助，学校规定除特殊情况外，导师在学校补助的钱外还应发放一定数量的钱，那是你导师决定的。", "timestamp": 1637039079, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2953158, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {"h": 842, "w": 1434}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Eve", "pid": 560424, "reply_to": 2952505, "tag": null, "text": "Re Carol: 树洞里之前发过", "timestamp": 1637039162, "type": "image", "url": "nc/ncflpp3zanm7xvwddqbq734ztyg5g6zd.jpeg"}, {"cid": 2953168, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Eve", "pid": 560424, "reply_to": 2952455, "tag": null, "text": "Re Bob: #427534\n学校资助体系研究生入学教育是讲过的，如果你不知道只能说明你没听。", "timestamp": 1637039216, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2953185, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Bob", "pid": 560424, "reply_to": 2953128, "tag": null, "text": "Re Eve: 我说的是，补助是补助，学费是学费", "timestamp": 1637039355, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2953191, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Bob", "pid": 560424, "reply_to": 2953168, "tag": null, "text": "Re Eve: 我也能从官网上，找到对于学费的一系列规定和标准", "timestamp": 1637039393, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2953211, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Bob", "pid": 560424, "reply_to": 2953168, "tag": null, "text": "Re Eve: 并且题目既然是研究生，那么既有学硕也有专硕，甚至还有非全日制", "timestamp": 1637039526, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2953251, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Eve", "pid": 560424, "reply_to": 2953191, "tag": null, "text": "Re Bob: 简而言之，国家规定，各学校应该收取学费，http://www.moe.gov.cn/jyb_xxgk/moe_1777/moe_1779/201305/t20130522_152217.html。其次，学校规定，收取的学费在学校资助中的基本奖助金退还。就这么简单，听不懂拉倒", "timestamp": 1637039767, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2953262, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Eve", "pid": 560424, "reply_to": 2953211, "tag": null, "text": "Re Bob: 最后，国家没有规定非全日制和专硕必须退学费，学校也没有规定，也没有任何一个学校这么做，除了那些招不到学生的学校", "timestamp": 1637039830, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2953298, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Eve", "pid": 560424, "reply_to": 2953211, "tag": null, "text": "Re Bob: 如果你觉得所有研究生应该退费，只能说那是你觉得，学校没必要按照你觉得运行。国家早就取消公费读研了", "timestamp": 1637039966, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2953305, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Bob", "pid": 560424, "reply_to": 2951752, "tag": null, "text": "我的观点也是应该对研究生收取学费呀", "timestamp": 1637040011, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2953309, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Bob", "pid": 560424, "reply_to": 2953298, "tag": null, "text": "Re Eve: 在我的第一条评论里就表示了呀", "timestamp": 1637040042, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2953342, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Eve", "pid": 560424, "reply_to": 2953309, "tag": null, "text": "Re Bob: 我明白你的意思了，抱歉", "timestamp": 1637040181, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2953355, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Eve", "pid": 560424, "reply_to": 2953309, "tag": null, "text": "Re Bob: 我只是想说，学术性学位是都以学校奖助金的形式退费了的，这也是之前学校说过的，所以也不能说研究生都不退", "timestamp": 1637040239, "type": "text", "url": ""}], "post": {"deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "likenum": 7, "pid": 560424, "reply": 23, "tag": null, "text": "好奇，为什么清华的研究生不退学费？", "timestamp": 1637024140, "type": "text", "updated_at": 1637040238, "url": "", "vote": {}}}